Hi Arron,
From the image you posted it look like you have a pre-1964 beam with a 
1966-67 anti-sway bar.  Take a look at the rubber snubber front beam part 211 
401 273 A in the obsolete bus parts book for 1963-67 buses.
Eric&Barb

